This paper deals with wireless communication in cellular networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.SY) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also involves modeling and analysis of communication systems, which falls under information theory (cs.IT). The use of energy harvesting is a key aspect of the paper, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as energy harvesting can be used to improve the security of wireless communication. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.NI and cs.IT, followed by cs.SY, cs.MM, and cs.CR.
